<p>
  Users opt in to receive SMS messages through a direct onboarding and hiring process managed by our staff.
  Phone numbers are collected during application, onboarding, or assignment setup, and explicit consent to receive
  operational text messages is obtained and documented in our internal system.
  Users are informed of the types of messages they will receive, that message frequency may vary, and that they may
  opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong>.
</p>
